Name: El Pescador
About the game: A funny and short platform challenge where the skill and the patience of any player will be tested. Advance through 16 levels full of enemies and obstacles to overcome. Enjoy 5 different worlds with their own characteristics and a unique boss to defeat. Finally, defeat the final boss with the help of your fishing rod.
